thread.title: Stephanie Parnell
thread.title_full: Harvard Business Services reviewed by Stephanie Parnell

author: Stephanie Parnell
title: Stephanie Parnell
text: Exceptional customer service. Polite and professional. I really appreciated the immediate contact once my order was place. My LLC was up and running in a matter of hours (so it seemed). Much sooner than I has expected which was a "gift" to me.
